                    to schedule your visit at Seaford Central Medical Clinic.
                </p>
                <div>
                    <a href="/appointments" class="btn btn-lg me-2 mb-2">
                        Book Online
                    </a>
                    <a href="tel:0397860008" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg mb-2"
                       style="border-radius: 14px 0px 14px 0px;">
                        <i class="fa fa-phone me-2"/>Call Us
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</template>

</odoo>
